snippet.title: Phodcast with Elvish: Yeh Love Triangle Hai? Aditi Mistry Confused Between Elvish aur Hardik Pandya?
snippet.description:
Welcome to Phod-Cast with Elvish Yadav—where the classic podcast gets a savage upgrade! 🎙🔥 In this game-changing show, Elvish doesn’t just sit down for interviews; he breaks the mold with humor, roasts, wild games, and juicy revelations from your favourite celebrities.

Model and influencer, Aditi Mistry, talks about her career, her controversial instagram posts and also about Urfi Javed, Sunny Leone and Hardik Pandya. She also wants to go gymming with Elvish Bhai

Nitish and Sundar added 127 runs for the eighth wicket to cut India's deficit to 116 after Australia's 474 in Melbourne.
Day 3 was Test cricket at its raw and pulsating best, a reminder of why the Australia-India rivalry stands at the pinnacle of the format. Reddy and Sundar fought back, but Australia remained in a strong position, poised to secure a significant first-innings lead.

હે મારા દિલ નો પતંગ જો.. (૨)
ફરરર ફરરર ફરરર ફરરર હે એ એ
ફરરર ઉડતો જાય જાનુ મારા દિલ નો પતંગ જો

હે દિલ વાલા પતંગ ઉપર નામ લખ્યુ તારુ
બીજ ના હાથ માં ના આવે તો હારુ
નકર પડી જાશે રંગ માં ભંગ 
જાનુ મારા દિલ પતંગ જો
ફરરર ઉડતો જાય જાનુ મારા દિલ નો પતંગ જો...

હે ઓઢીલે ઓઢીલે ઓઢણી તારી ઓઢીલે
તડકા માં ગાલ કાળા પડશે વાત મોનીલે
અરે આવીજા આવીજા ધાબે મારા આવીજા

ધાબે મારા આવે તો તને ખવડાવુ
હે ખાશુ ચિક્કી ને ઉડાડ શુ પતંગ
જાનુ મારા દિલ નો પતંગ જો
હે ઇતો ઉડતો ઉડતો આયો જાનુ મારા દિલ નો પતંગ જો...

હો લપેટ લપેટ કહી ગળુ ના બેહાડશો 
વિક્સ ની ગોળીયો તમે ખીસા માં રાખજો
હો બેનપણીયો ભાળી દોડ બહુ કરોશો
ઓઠે ઓઠે જઈ તમે મને તાકોશો
હે તારો પતંગ હુ કિનીયા તુ મારી
ઉડી જવાની ભેળા કરશુ તૈયારી
હે મારી જોડે તુ બાંધીલે સંબંધ
જાનુ મારા દિલ નો પતંગ જો
હે પછી પ્રેમ ના લડાવીયે પેચ
જાનુ મારા દિલ નો પતંગ જો
ફરરર ઉડતો જાય જાનુ મારા દિલ નો પતંગ જો
હે ઉડતો ઉડતો આયો ધાબે તારા દિલ નો પતંગ જો...

snippet.title: Ennu Swantham Punyalan Trailer |  Mahesh Madhu | Arjun Ashokan | Balu Varghese | Anaswara Rajan
snippet.description:
Presenting the Official Trailer Of ‘’Ennu Swantham Punyalan, Directed by debutant Mahesh Madhu. Starring Arjun Ashokan, Balu Varghese, and Anaswara Rajan in exciting new roles, the film is written by Samji M Antony. Produced by Ligo John under the banner of Truth Seekers Productions and distributed by Listin Stephan's Magic Frames, the film features music by Sam C.S. and an impressive supporting cast, including Renji Panicker, Baiju, and Althaf.

Mark your calendars—Ennu Swantham Punyalan hits theaters on January 10, 2025!

snippet.title: SHIVA SHIVA | Lyrical | Kannada | KD | KVN Production | Prem's | AJ | Dhruva Sarja |Reeshma| Suprith
snippet.description:
Presenting Shiva Shiva Lyrical Song From The Movie KD-The Devil  Starring: Dhruva Sarja, Reeshma Nanaiah, Shilpa Shetty & Others Exclusive Only On Anand Audio Official Youtube Channel..!!! 
----------------------------------------------
#KD #KDTHEDEVIL  #KVNProductions #shivashiva #shivashivakannada #trending #prems  #jogiprem #kdfirstsingle #kdsong #arjunjanya #kailashkher  #shilpashetty  #ramesharavind #vravichandran  #reeshmananaiah #dhruvasarja  #manjugowdabs  #showmanprem #youtube #anandaudio
----------------------------------------------
Song : Shiva Shiva Lyrical Song
Singers : Prem's, Kailash Kher
Lyricist : Manjunath BS
----------------------------------------------
To Listen On Your Favourite Music Streaming Platform
♪ Spotify : https://tinyurl.com/yc5wcnuv
♪ Jiosaavn : https://tinyurl.com/2cd9efn6
♪ Hungama : https://tinyurl.com/4shtadcr
♪ Amazon : https://tinyurl.com/2unc9dyv
♪ Gaana : https://tinyurl.com/2jrtd5t7
♪ Youtube Music : https://tinyurl.com/2dpeus2y
♪ Insta Reels : https://tinyurl.com/4cmbrzxk
----------------------------------------------
ಪಲ್ಲವಿ :
ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್..ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್..
ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ..
ಶಿವನೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ, ಶಿವಾ..
ಶಿವ ಶಿವ ಶಿವ ಶಿವ ಶಿವ ಶಿವ
ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ..
ಶಿವನೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ, ಶಿವಾ..
ಚರಣ 1:
ಹತ್ತೂರಿನ ಒಡೆಯ ನೀನು, ಗೊತ್ತೇನೋ ಯಾರು ನಿಂಗೆ...
ಸೈನ್ಯಾನೆ ಇಲ್ಲ ಇವನ್ಗೆ, ಹೊಂಟವ್ನೆ ರಾಜ ನಂಗೆ..
ಬೆಳಗಾಗೋದ್ರಲ್ಲೇ ಬೆಳೆದಾ...ಬೆಳಗಾಗೋದ್ರಲ್ಲೇ ಬೆಳೆದು ಫೇಮಸ್ಸು ಆಗೋದ್ನಲ್ಲ..
ನಾನು ನಾನ್ ಅಂದೋರ್ಗೆಲ್ಲಾ ತೊಡೆತಟ್ಟಿ ನಿಂತವ್ನ್ ನೋಡ್ಲಾ..
ಬೆಳೆದ ಬೆಳೆದ ಬೆಳೆದ ನೋಡೋ..
ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ..
ಶಿವನೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ, ಶಿವಾ..
ಚರಣ 2:
ದೌಲತ್ತಲ್ ಮೆರದೋರೆಲ್ಲ ಹಿಸ್ಟರಿ ಲಿ ಉಳಿದೆಯಿಲ್ಲ..
ಕಾಲೇಳೆಯೋಕ್ ಬಂದೋರೆಲ್ಲ ಕಾಲ ಕೆಳ್ಗೆ ಉಳ್ದೊದ್ರಲ್ಲ
ನೀನ್ ಅಂತೋನ್ ಅಲ್ವೇ ಅಲ್ಲ...ನೀನ್ ಅಂತೋನ್ ಅಲ್ವೇ ಅಲ್ಲ... ನಿನ್ನಂಗೆ ಯಾರು ಇಲ್ಲ..
ಬಕೇಟಾ ಹಿಡಿಯೋರ್ನೆಲ್ಲ ಸೈಡಿಟ್ಟು ಹೋಯ್ತಯೀರ್ಲಾ ..
ಬೆಳೆದ ಬೆಳೆದ ಬೆಳೆದ ನೋಡೋ..
ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್..ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್..
ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ..
ಶಿವನೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ, ಶಿವಾ..
ಶಿವಾ..ಶಿವಾ..ಶಿವಾ..ಶಿವಾ..ಶಿವಾ..
----------------------------------------------

Keyboard & Rhythm Programming : V Sukumar 
Flute : Naveen

snippet.title: సూపర్ హిట్ న్యూ ఇయర్ స్పెషల్ నాన్ వెజ్ తాలి | Exciting New Year Special Non Veg Thali @VismaiFood
snippet.description:
Hello Foodies !! Welcome to Vismai Food !!.

Today we are presenting the new year special exciting non veg thali in Vismai Food's non-vegetarian thali series. This non-vegetarian thali can be prepared easily at home. This non-vegetarian thali includes six amazing recipes: Mutton dum biryani, Gongura Chicken, Carrot Anjeer Semiya Payasam, Mustard Fish, Tawa Chicken Roast, Brinjal Curry. This non-vegetarian recipe is super perfect for this coming happy newyear year party, weekend parties, birthdays, family function and any other events. If you are looking for a amazing non veg meals recipe, this vismai food's special nonveg thali is an excellent choice. Simply follow the steps and procedures outlined in this video to prepare a perfect thali at any time. All of the ingredients are readily available. Take a look at the ingredient list below. Do try this amazing non-veg thali and leave your feedback in the comments section. You can also share the photos on Instagram by tagging Vismai Food.

#happynewyear #nonvegthali #newyearthali #nonvegthaliseries #weekendthalirecipe #gongurachicken #kajupulao #vismaifood #vismaifoodrecipes #vismaifoodthaliseries

Detailed recipes with Ingredients and Method in English & Telugu visit https://www.vismaifood.com

Check out our kitchenware, appliances, utensils, and ingredients by the following link: 

Vismai Food's Amazon Store 🛒: https://www.amazon.in/shop/vismaifood

Ingredients:
For Tawa Chicken Roast:
12-15 Dry Chilies
12-15 Garlic pods
1 inch Ginger
1 Star anise
1.5 inch Cinnamon
1/2 tsp Cumin
3-4 Cloves
1 tsp Stone flower
Salt
1/4 tsp Turmeric
3 tbsp Oil for Marination
1 Lemon Juice
750 gms Tandoori cut Chicken
1/4 cup for Roastings

For Mustard Fish:
3 tbsp Soaked Mustard 
2 Green Chilies
1/2 inch Ginger
5-6 Garlic Pods (grind to a fine paste)
500 gms Boneless Fish
Salt
1/4 tsp Turmeric
1/2 tbsp Chili Powder
1/2 tsp Black Pepper
2 tbsp Corn flour
1 tbsp Maida
Oil for Deep Frying

For Carrot Anjeer Semiya Payasam:
1/2 litre Milk
3/4 cup Semiya
1/2 cup Carrot gratings
5-6 Anjeer choppings
3 tbsp Ghee
1/2 litre Water
3/4 cup-1 cup Condensed Milk
1/2 tsp Vanilla essence
3 tbsp Cashews
2 tbsp Raisins

For Gongura Chicken:
1/3 cup Oil
7-8 Garlic pods
1/2 tsp Cumin
2 Dry Chilies
2 sprigs Curry leaves
1/2 cup Onion choppings
2 slit green chilies
1 tbsp Ginger garlic paste
1/2 Kilo Chicken
1 Tomato slices
2 tbsp Chili Powder
1/2 tsp Turmeric
1 tsp Coriander powder
1 tsp Roasted Cumin powder
1/2 tsp Garam Masala
Salt
200 gms Gongura
1.1/4 cup Water

For Mutton Dum Biryani:
1/2 kilo MUtton
50 gms Mutton Fat
1/4 cup Oil
1/4 cup Ghee
7-8 Green Cardamoms
8-10 Cloves
3 inch Cinnamon
1 Star anise
2 tbsp Stone flower
3-4 Bay leaves
1 cup malai curd
1.5 tbsp Shahi Jeera
2 Onion slices
3 Green Chilies pieces
2 tbsp Ginger garlic paste
2 Tomato cubes
1 litre Water
Fist full Mint & Coriander
1/2 kilo Rice
1/4 cup Milk
2 Lemon Juice
2.5 tbsp Chili powder
1/2 tbsp Coriander powder
1/2 tbsp Roasted Cumin Powder
1/2 tbsp Garam masala
1/2 tsp Turmeric
Salt
1/4 cup Ghee

For Brinjal Curry:
3 tbsp Peanuts 
2 tsp kaju 
1.5 tbsp Sesame 
1/4 to 1/3 cup Oil 
6-7 Slit Brinjals 
1/2 tsp Mustard 
2 pinches Fenugreek 
1/2 tsp Black pepper
 8-10 Garlic pods 
2 sprigs Curry leaves 
1 cup Onion choppings
 2 Tomato choppings 
1 tbsp Coriander powder
 1.1/4 tbsp Chili powder 
1/4 tsp Turmeric 
Salt 
1/4 cup Tamarind extract (extracted from lemon size tamarind) 
2 cups Water Coriander choppings

Follow us on Social Media:

https://twitter.com/VismaiF
https://www.instagram.com/vismaifoodies/
https://www.facebook.com/Vismai-Food-...

Vismai Food Team:
Executive Producer: Swetha Paruchuri
Music: Kalyani Malik
Camera: Phani Sudhir
Editing: Koteswar
Social Media Manager: A.K

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

snippet.title: पंकजा मुंडे, धनंजय मुंडे यांच्यासोबत फोटो, कमरेला बंदूक लावणारे परळीतला Nikhil Kailas Phad कोण आहे?
snippet.description:
#NikhilPhad #KailasPhad #Gun #KailasPhad #SantoshDeshmukh #Beed #Parli #PankajaMunde #DhananjayMunde #WalmikKarad  

बीडच्या मस्साजोग मध्ये घडलेल्या सरपंच संतोष देशमुख यांच्या खूनानं महाराष्ट्र हादरुन निघाला आहे. या घटनेमुळे बीडमधील कायदा सुव्यवस्थेचे तीन तेरा वाजलेले असल्याचं दिसून येतंय. भाजप आमदार सुरेश धस, आमदार संदीप क्षीरसागर यांनी या प्रकरणावरुन मंत्री धनंजय मुंडेंचे निकटवर्तीय वाल्मिक कराडांना लक्ष केलं जातंय. आवादा वाईन्ड मिलच्या खंडणीचा प्रकरणात मुंडेंचे निकटवर्तीय वाल्मिक कराडांवर खंडणीचा गुन्हा दाखल झालेला आहे. यावरुन मंत्री असलेल्या धनंजय मुंडेंवर सरकारमधील आमदारांसह विरोधीपक्ष त्यांना मंत्रिपदापासून दूर ठेवा मागणी करत होता. पण आता त्यांना पालकमंत्रीपदापासून दूर ठेवा असा सूर दिसत आहे. अशातच सामाजिक कार्यकर्त्या अंजली दमानियांनी कायदा सुव्यवस्थेवरुन सवाल उपस्थित केले आहेत. 


🔴लॉग इन करा: https://www.mumbaitak.in/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/mumbai_tak
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLzHYo6L3SZJGBWc_BPfqMt5Yq24d_AXCa

#maharashtra #marathi #marathinews

इंडिया टुडेच्या मुंबई तक या मराठी युट्यूब चॅनलवर आपलं स्वागत. इंडिया टुडे ग्रुपचे मॅगझिन, इंडिया टुडे टीव्ही आणि आज तक हे लोकप्रिय न्यूज चॅनल आपल्याला माहितीच आहे. त्यानंतर आता खास मराठी प्रेक्षकांसाठी आपण भारतीय प्रादेशिक भाषेतलं पहिलं मराठी चॅनल घेऊन आलोय. महाराष्ट्रासह राष्ट्रीय आणि आंतरराष्ट्रीयस्तरावरील महत्वाच्या बातम्या आणि घडामोडी आपल्याला अगदी सोप्या शब्दांत समजावण्याचा आमचा प्रयत्न असणार आहे. 
Namskar, Welcome to India Today group’s new Marathi YouTube channel – Mumbai Tak. Get all the latest important stories and updates from in and around Maharashtra in Marathi. Stay Tuned to Mumbai Tak for current affairs, politics, sports, business, entertainment, literature and many more in Marathi.

बीडच्या मस्साजोग मध्ये घडलेल्या सरपंच संतोष देशमुख यांच्या खूनानं महाराष्ट्र हादरुन निघाला आहे. या घटनेमुळे बीडमधील कायदा सुव्यवस्थेचे तीन तेरा वाजलेले असल्याचं दिसून येतंय. भाजप आमदार सुरेश धस, आमदार संदीप क्षीरसागर यांनी या प्रकरणावरुन मंत्री धनंजय मुंडेंचे निकटवर्तीय वाल्मिक कराडांना लक्ष केलं जातंय. आवादा वाईन्ड मिलच्या खंडणीचा प्रकरणात मुंडेंचे निकटवर्तीय वाल्मिक कराडांवर खंडणीचा गुन्हा दाखल झालेला आहे. यावरुन मंत्री असलेल्या धनंजय मुंडेंवर सरकारमधील आमदारांसह विरोधीपक्ष त्यांना मंत्रिपदापासून दूर ठेवा मागणी करत होता. पण आता त्यांना पालकमंत्रीपदापासून दूर ठेवा असा सूर दिसत आहे. अशातच सामाजिक कार्यकर्त्या अंजली दमानियांनी कायदा सुव्यवस्थेवरुन सवाल उपस्थित केले आहेत.

snippet.title: MELBOURNE, VIKRANT GUPTA DAY 4: GABBA से लो inspiration, New Ball करेगा Indian क़िस्मत का फ़ैसला
snippet.description:
MELBOURNE, VIKRANT GUPTA ,DAY 4, REPORT: The Boxing Day Test has lived up to the billing. After four days of intense back-and-forth action, all three results are possible on the final day of the Test match. There was nothing to separate the two teams on Day 4 in Melbourne as they threw punches at each other on a day that ebbed and flowed, much like the way the series has panned out Down Under.
The session pie on Day 4 might show both India and Australia shared honours, but deep down, India will know they let go off an opportunity to take Australia by the scruff of the neck. Australia were reeling at 91 for 6 in the second session, but their never-say-die attitude shone through in helping them finish with 228 for 9, and with a lead of 333 runs.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4279 | 27 Dec 2024 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4279: Chotelal Ki Bhavishyavaani
--------------------------------------------------------
Chotelal, disguised as an astrologer, advises Bhide to stop worrying about Sonu's marriage now, in an attempt to help Sonu escape the situation. Will Bhide be believe him?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4279 | 27 Dec 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1000302734

snippet.title: Raghuvir आये Kartik का Case लड़ने | Mangal Lakshmi | मंगल लक्ष्मी | Sneak Peek
snippet.description:
📲 Download JioCinema: https://bit.ly/3Be09Z3

Raghuvir आये Kartik का Case लड़ने | Mangal Lakshmi | मंगल लक्ष्मी | Sneak Peek
Mangal foils Saumya’s party plans, leading to her accusing him of poisoning halwa to oust her. A livid Saumya accuses Mangal of poisoning the halwa in a bid to oust her from the house. Meanwhile, during Kartik’s hearing, Jia’s foul play delays the lawyer, but Raghuvir arrives last minute, securing time to gather evidence.
-----
Mangal Lakshmi unfolds as a poignant narrative, delving into the profound connection shared between two sisters, Mangal and Lakshmi. Set against life's myriad experiences, the story chronicles Mangal's odyssey in search of the ideal match, a 'dulha', for her cherished sibling, Lakshmi. As the tale progresses, it gracefully illustrates the intricacies of love, the resilience required to overcome trials, and the unwavering resolve that propels Mangal forward on her quest. Through the lens of sisterhood's enduring bond and the inexorable force of destiny, the narrative unfurls a tapestry of emotions, ultimately celebrating the timeless allure of fate in uniting kindred spirits.

snippet.title: Bhide ने डाला Dr. Hathi पे बाल्टी भर पानी | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | New Year Countdown
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Bhide is out in his living room, relaxing as he reads the newspaper. But soon his peace gets disrupted by Tapu Sena's constant noise and he tells them to keep quiet! Find out more by watching the episode.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #newyearcountdown #newyear2025 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch more clips from New Year Countdown: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G2wI91egSQvmRpJMIXBOmIa

Four men break into Dhanraj's house and the burglar alarm starts ringing. When the neighbors come to check what has happened, all four men start firing in the air and leave the place. One of the neighbors calls CID as they spot a thief lying inside the house. 

Show Name: CID

• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy

• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.
